PrecisAmendment to the DETERMINATION OF COUNTRY OF ORIGIN FOR THE PURPOSES OF MARKING GOODS (NAFTA COUNTRIES) REGULATIONS which adds eight horticultural nursery items to the list of goods in Schedule I that, upon importation, are to be marked with their country of origin, effective August 15, 1995.

precis:
Amendment to the DETERMINATION OF COUNTRY OF ORIGIN FOR THE PURPOSES OF
MARKING GOODS (NAFTA COUNTRIES) REGULATIONS which adds eight horticultural
nursery items to the list of goods in Schedule I that, upon importation,
are to be marked with their country of origin, effective August 15, 1995.
